<h2>Medical Synonym Lists from Medieval Provence: Shem Tov ben Isaac of Tortosa, Sefer ha-Shimmush, Book 29 (Monographie)</h2>
<h3>Part 1: Edition and Commentary of List 1 (Hebrew - Arabic - Romance/Latin)</h3>
